title: Spacious walk-in closets, Balcony or patio for every unit
posting_body: ['Camber Apartments', '1231 NE McWilliams Rd, Bremerton, WA, 98311', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 31', 'OR Text', '31', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'ANCHORED IN COMMUNITY', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 783 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'A respite from the city.', 'A city surrounded by one of the most breathtaking landscapes in America.', 'Bremerton was once dominated by shipbuilding, and the foothills to the north where Camber crests a two-lane road and is an easy drive to a bustling and historic downtown.', 'Walk to what you need or drive to whatever you want—this location has it all, and everything is within reach.', 'Your Pacific Northwest retreat.', 'Features', '- Quartz counters with high-end finishes', '- Lush park-like views', '- Balcony or patio for every unit', '- Washer and dryer in every unit', '- Luxury vinyl flooring', '- Spacious walk-in closets', '- Stainless steel appliances', '- Primary suites', 'Community Amenities', '- Theatre-inspired media room', "- Clubhouse with caterer's kitchen", '- Play areas', '- Parcel Pending', '- Massive Fire Pits', '- Billiards, ping pong, and air hockey', '- Fitness center', '- Integrated trails', '- Controlled access, gated entry', '- Three seasons room for entertaining', '- Smoke Free', '- Dog park *Coming in 2023*', '- Covered outdoor spa', '- BBQs picnic shelters', '- Heated resort-style pool', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Sunday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Policy Type: Cat, Dog', 'Max Number of Pets: 2', 'Pet deposit fee min/max: $300 - $450', 'Pet monthly rent min/max: $25 - $50', 'Pet policy fee min/max: $200 - $400', 'Income Requirements:', 'Three times rent.', 'Bremerton apartments kitsap apartments kitsap peninsula apartments', 'OaI4Wfawo']
